import { Container, Left, Header, Icon } from 'native-base'
import React from 'react'
import { View, Text } from 'react-native'
import { Appbar, Title, Button } from 'react-native-paper'

export default function Home({ navigation }) {
    return (
        <View>
            <Appbar.Header style={{backgroundColor: "#fff"}} >
                <Appbar.Action size={35} icon="menu" onPress={() => navigation.openDrawer()} />
            </Appbar.Header>
            
            <View>
                {/*Presentation */}
                <View style={{backgroundColor: "#1c2295", height: 125, width: "100%"}}>
                    <Title style={{
                        fontSize: 30,
                        alignItems: "center",
                        textAlign: "center",
                        marginTop: 50,
                        color: "#fff",
                        textDecorationLine: "underline"
                    }}>Présenation</Title>
                </View>
                <Button onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Dashboard')}>
                    Press me
                </Button>
            </View>
            { /* Visualisation des données */ }

            { /* Gestes barriéres */ }

            { /* Bottom Navigation */ }            
        </View>
    )
}
